    popt4jlib.SA
    Simulated Annealing Algorithms Parallel Implementation.
  • Classes in popt4jlib.SA used by popt4jlib.SA 
    Class and Description
    DSA
    The DSA class implements a parallel Simulated Annealing algorithm for the minimization of a function to be passed in as argument object implementing the FunctionIntf argument of the minimize(f) method.
    DSAIndividual
    auxiliary class, not part of the public API.
    DSAThread
    auxiliary class not part of the public API
    DSAThreadAux
    auxiliary class not part of the public API
    SAScheduleIntf
    defines the contract for a temperature cooling schedule -primarily depending on the outer-most iteration number of the SA process, but also possibly on other parameters and/or variable values that may be passed via the Hashtable second argument of the main method of the interface.
